article_title: Ukraine aid from US in doubt after failed Senate vote
sentence: "I  do  not  believe  we  should  be  appropriating  over  $10  billion  for  the  right-wing  extremist  Netanyahu  government  to  continue  its  current  military  approach,"  Mr  Sanders  said,  referring  to  Israeli  Prime  Minister  Benjamin  Netanyahu's  ongoing  campaign  in  the  Gaza  strip,  which  has  so  far  killed  thousands  of  civilians.
